{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "61b9bfc6-d88d-473e-bf9a-089fbc126f99",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 1 06 Glow for It",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "25bf9665-7883-467c-ac81-5e1a943e36aa",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "77e1ddff-4996-4051-a78d-838c39d64e98",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c408dde1-9e7d-4b38-9f27-d34f91a12891",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For today's lesson, you will all learn the basics of a new spell - <i>Glow for It</i> or, as it is more commonly called, <i>Glow.</i> This spell creates an aura of light around your body, allowing you to see better in dark places.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "6ecb74e2-6d42-4e05-b36d-67e6d2f5b90e",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "What makes this particularly useful is that this is a light only you will be able to see. Thus, in dark and dangerous places, you will not call unwanted attention to yourself.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "6aab4ad3-8b92-4cab-9346-4b29ebdec4a5",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We will be first studying the rune for \"Self,\" which is a symbol for yourself. This is used whenever you want a spell to focus upon your body rather than another person or object.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "20ef5b2a-922f-4b8e-9515-73cbef24ccd9",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We will then work on the rune for \"Light.\" Finally, when we combine the two runes, we will have the symbol for the Glow spell.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2fb514ac-b2b7-4ed7-9ee8-560731f68d1f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "In tomorrow's class, we will be making a runestone to allow you to cast the spell. Are there any questions or comments?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "4",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3aa9f8ca-11dc-4331-91f2-62f4cd8b2714",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "86ba7b5a-d3c3-4f63-928c-2f3a8354e078",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "43ccd3c4-2d13-403e-bea1-f5c20d8dcd4f",
                            "text": "Ask About Helping Others With the Spell",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "61b5b359-6228-4d82-af5b-6d35036bc393",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Is there some way to cast the spell so that other people with you can see the light, too? I'd like to be able to help my friends out.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5cefab6f-9254-4934-b33a-c61590f4357c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "What a nice thought! Sadly, while there is a similar spell using the same rune for Light combined with other runes that makes a visible light, it is a more advanced spell and we will not be covering it in this class.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "d2709730-8548-4209-8c10-072aa3a90722",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "30",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "cb95526e-4fa8-45e1-8707-f0e7ddc2aac7",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "9ba52fab-8b06-413a-8add-37dd2dd22b62",
                            "text": "Ask About Combining Runes",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "e05d7e68-9496-4df6-b5ae-2916c9a8cd32",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "If you combine the Light rune from the Glow spell with the Magic rune from the Sense Magic spell, could you make a magical light?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5d478e42-9d57-4561-9601-ab3c66f9bf3c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Technically speaking, the Glow spell already creates a magical light surrounding your body. If you cast Sense Magic upon someone using the Glow spell, you will be able to detect the spell.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d053abf7-3294-4d8f-b607-2fc2435b2e49",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, the Light rune you are learning for the Glow spell is not a description but a command. You are commanding your body to glow rather than creating a light around your body.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5de5bf6e-9525-49ae-87e8-43c5e3d9cd7a",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "A Wizard has to memorize hundreds of specific runes and understand the semantic differences between them in order to cast spells. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "05bf492b-ed8c-469e-a07a-d7a0a986043b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Since this is a Magic class rather than a Wizard class, I will try to keep the runes you have to learn both simple and useful.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "83bed11a-89a4-4a82-9056-6b717d1e088b",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "30",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "651e2837-9154-45e7-9760-bd5a375f0748",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "10",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f6d69dc1-c4d4-4469-9f2e-fdf6317a873d",
                            "text": "Ask Something Silly About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0fcfcec8-7554-43bf-a579-9103b685f635",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "When a Wizard gets wrapped up in his work, would you say that he is spellbound?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "408d98cb-3c0c-451f-baf3-f25b050acedb",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wizards always get wrapped up in their work.. It's an occupational hazard.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "280d00d8-bd55-4f28-86e0-4aea2445ba72",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So I guess Wizards do things just for the spell of it?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2d4c38d5-0786-46f4-8361-c57c1de1c2d7",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You could say that.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "eab255b8-a5f7-4bd7-95f1-5e2e1a2e7f3e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "30",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "8c9173d7-109c-4f45-8de3-d3e325aeadb5",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
